        &trans        &trans        &kp PLUS      &kp LEFT_PARENTHESIS  &kp LEFT_BRACE      &kp RIGHT_BRACE    &kp RIGHT_PARENTHESIS  &kp EQUAL  &trans  &trans
&trans  &trans        &trans        &trans        &kp MINUS             &kp LEFT_BRACKET    &kp RIGHT_BRACKET  &kp UNDER              &trans     &trans  &trans  &kp PIPE
                                    &trans        &trans                &trans              &mo 3              &kp KP_N0              &trans
